1
00:00:26,370 --> 00:00:27,900
[This work is based on historical events,]

2
00:00:27,900 --> 00:00:29,570
[but all depiction of details of their lives and motives are fictional.]

3
00:00:40,685 --> 00:00:42,928
I've missed you so much,

4
00:00:46,101 --> 00:00:47,825
Deok Im.

5
00:01:18,916 --> 00:01:21,706
Will you be mine if I command so?

6
00:01:21,706 --> 00:01:26,466
I shall… if you command so.

7
00:01:26,466 --> 00:01:29,276
Would that be what you wish?

8
00:01:29,276 --> 00:01:31,328
Perhaps.

9
00:01:32,968 --> 00:01:36,209
Perhaps that is what I desire.

10
00:01:38,912 --> 00:01:41,290
But even more than that,

11
00:01:42,770 --> 00:01:45,600
I hope to keep my place.

12
00:01:47,110 --> 00:01:49,403
That is the answer I expected.

13
00:02:17,200 --> 00:02:20,519
Her Highness the Queen Dowager is waiting.

14
00:02:39,178 --> 00:02:43,100
I didn't expect your visit at such a late hour.

15
00:02:43,100 --> 00:02:46,896
There is something I wish to discuss with Your Highness.

16
00:02:46,896 --> 00:02:50,125
Is it that urgent?

17
00:02:51,610 --> 00:02:56,512
I am but a concubine of His Majesty.

18
00:02:56,512 --> 00:02:58,950
Without a child,

19
00:02:58,950 --> 00:03:01,420
there will be no purpose for me.

20
00:03:02,607 --> 00:03:05,430
And I will be miserably abandoned.

21
00:03:06,693 --> 00:03:13,011
Your Highness is the only one who can offer me help.

22
00:03:16,231 --> 00:03:18,760
I beg of you.

23
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:22,190
Have pity on me.

24
00:03:34,885 --> 00:03:36,940
It pains my heart…

25
00:03:37,760 --> 00:03:40,000
when you cry.

26
00:03:41,595 --> 00:03:44,322
So much so that I can't bear it.

27
00:03:45,703 --> 00:03:47,842
I've missed you so much...

28
00:03:54,684 --> 00:03:56,275
Deok Im.

29
00:03:58,207 --> 00:03:59,934
Brother.

30
00:04:05,750 --> 00:04:07,690
[Episode 16]

31
00:04:12,500 --> 00:04:17,702
Don't you have a better way to spend your vacation than spend time with me?

32
00:04:17,702 --> 00:04:22,223
What are you talking about? This is what I most wanted to do.

33
00:04:30,123 --> 00:04:31,522
Here.

34
00:04:32,786 --> 00:04:34,420
What's this?

35
00:04:35,484 --> 00:04:38,090
I passed the examination.

36
00:04:38,090 --> 00:04:40,410
I will be serving at the Royal Artillery.

37
00:04:40,410 --> 00:04:45,230
You'll be a soldier, just like our father was.

38
00:04:45,230 --> 00:04:47,541
It's all thanks to you.

39
00:04:48,268 --> 00:04:50,417
Thank you, Deok Im.

40
00:04:55,714 --> 00:04:58,481
And you have my thanks, too.

41
00:04:58,481 --> 00:05:02,114
I have long waited for a day like this.

42
00:05:04,307 --> 00:05:06,307
Is there anything else you want?

43
00:05:07,123 --> 00:05:08,684
Take a look at these.

44
00:05:08,684 --> 00:05:10,820
Well then…

45
00:05:12,890 --> 00:05:15,536
No. How about this one?

46
00:05:18,500 --> 00:05:20,490
Your Majesty.

47
00:05:20,490 --> 00:05:24,430
A message has arrived from Queen Dowager.

48
00:05:24,433 --> 00:05:29,995
Her brother, Kim Ki Ju, has fallen ill.

49
00:05:30,602 --> 00:05:36,498
This message is from your royal elder and seems to express her desperate plea.

50
00:05:36,498 --> 00:05:41,317
Wouldn't it be wise to release Kim Ki Ju from exile?

51
00:05:41,317 --> 00:05:47,014
For this, I shall pay Queen Dowager a visit myself

52
00:05:47,014 --> 00:05:48,485
and deliver my answer.

53
00:05:48,485 --> 00:05:53,700
Your Majesty, please let us know of your intention.

54
00:05:53,700 --> 00:05:57,900
Do you intend to ignore

55
00:05:57,900 --> 00:06:01,582
the request from Queen Dowager?

56
00:06:01,582 --> 00:06:07,695
You must serve Queen Dowager well and do your duties as a grandson.

57
00:06:07,695 --> 00:06:09,434
Assistant Counselor.

58
00:06:10,289 --> 00:06:11,478
Yes, Your Majesty.

59
00:06:11,478 --> 00:06:15,942
Do you know of the saying,

60
00:06:17,701 --> 00:06:21,961
"Bulgageun, bulgawon."

61
00:06:23,716 --> 00:06:29,202
"One should not draw too close, nor stray too far from another."

62
00:06:31,589 --> 00:06:37,714
I hope you understand why I speak of this.

63
00:06:38,802 --> 00:06:43,317
I will be disappointed if you don't.

64
00:06:47,483 --> 00:06:50,156
Let us discuss our next agenda.

65
00:07:02,501 --> 00:07:06,451
There are things in this world that are not easily reversed.

66
00:07:06,451 --> 00:07:12,607
One's feelings. When they are hurt, it's hard to undo what's been done.

67
00:07:12,607 --> 00:07:14,302
Your Majesty,

68
00:07:15,286 --> 00:07:20,386
if my brother dies, I will hold a grudge against you.

69
00:07:23,914 --> 00:07:28,876
I will send the royal doctor to tend to Kim Ki Ju's illness.

70
00:07:28,876 --> 00:07:34,800
Could you not have trust in me for even once?

71
00:07:35,612 --> 00:07:38,204
I gave my trust to Hong Deok Ro.

72
00:07:39,902 --> 00:07:42,802
I knew well how it was going to turn out,

73
00:07:43,585 --> 00:07:46,933
but I really wanted to put my trust in him.

74
00:07:47,581 --> 00:07:51,233
And I will not let myself make the same mistake again.

75
00:07:54,326 --> 00:07:58,105
Your brother is the leader of the Noron faction.
(T/N: the conservative political faction)

76
00:07:58,105 --> 00:08:04,263
If he were to return, it would jeopardize the political balance I wish to achieve.

77
00:08:06,623 --> 00:08:09,378
And I cannot let that happen.

78
00:08:09,378 --> 00:08:14,889
I hope nothing happens to my brother.

79
00:08:14,889 --> 00:08:19,727
That is what I sincerely hope for.

80
00:08:19,727 --> 00:08:24,628
For myself, and for Your Majesty, as well.

81
00:08:31,427 --> 00:08:34,977
Visit Concubine Hwabin at 8 o'clock tonight.

82
00:08:37,475 --> 00:08:40,420
This is not for your sake,

83
00:08:40,420 --> 00:08:43,300
but for someone else's.

84
00:08:43,309 --> 00:08:45,619
It is someone that I cherished once,

85
00:08:45,619 --> 00:08:50,323
someone I still cherish until now.

86
00:08:55,897 --> 00:08:58,384
The King finally spoke,

87
00:08:58,384 --> 00:09:03,814
"If Pyeong Guk were a woman, how would he have fought so valiantly on the battlefield?"

88
00:09:03,814 --> 00:09:09,517
"But Pyeong Guk's skin is fair and the figure is slender, "

89
00:09:09,517 --> 00:09:14,117
- "...it is a bit suspicious."
- Why won't you serve me?

90
00:09:16,904 --> 00:09:18,902
Why is that

91
00:09:21,008 --> 00:09:24,434
I could not take you away from His Majesty?

92
00:09:25,688 --> 00:09:28,320
But if it's Concubine Hwabin…

93
00:09:34,591 --> 00:09:36,832
Will you serve me, Deok Im?

94
00:09:37,585 --> 00:09:42,006
Pledge your loyalty to me as you did to His Majesty.

95
00:09:42,006 --> 00:09:46,397
I will become a better mistress than Hwabin.

96
00:09:46,397 --> 00:09:48,783
I am sorry, Your Highness.

97
00:09:48,783 --> 00:09:53,132
My answer remains the same.

98
00:10:11,497 --> 00:10:15,198
In the past, my intention was to use you

99
00:10:15,198 --> 00:10:19,387
for you have the favor of His Majesty.

100
00:10:19,387 --> 00:10:23,840
So I wanted to have you by my side.

101
00:10:26,382 --> 00:10:29,104
You probably knew that, too.

102
00:10:35,284 --> 00:10:37,410
But it's different now.

103
00:10:38,118 --> 00:10:40,800
You are enough as you are.

104
00:10:41,582 --> 00:10:43,230
All I want is…

105
00:10:44,007 --> 00:10:47,724
a friend like you to be by my side

106
00:10:47,724 --> 00:10:50,418
in my long, lonely palace life.

107
00:10:53,200 --> 00:10:58,018
To be a friend of yours is an honor too lofty for me.

108
00:10:59,291 --> 00:11:03,696
Please forgive my refusal.

109
00:11:04,881 --> 00:11:06,620
I take it

110
00:11:07,710 --> 00:11:09,910
that you do not wish so.

111
00:11:10,919 --> 00:11:13,027
My apologies.

112
00:11:18,511 --> 00:11:20,743
That's a shame.

113
00:11:20,743 --> 00:11:24,330
I've always enjoyed your reading.

114
00:11:33,193 --> 00:11:35,227
It is a shame, indeed.

115
00:11:45,952 --> 00:11:47,685
What are you doing?

116
00:11:47,685 --> 00:11:49,448
Why are you doing this?

117
00:11:49,448 --> 00:11:51,595
We're only doing what we were commanded to do.

118
00:11:51,595 --> 00:11:54,893
Commanded? By whom?

119
00:11:57,094 --> 00:12:00,997
Your Highness the Concubine Hwabin, why are you doing this to me?

120
00:12:00,997 --> 00:12:03,794
I am an official palace maid.

121
00:12:03,794 --> 00:12:08,075
If you find me guilty in any way, you would have to refer me

122
00:12:08,075 --> 00:12:09,909
to the disciplinary court lady.

123
00:12:09,909 --> 00:12:14,011
You will have a chance to explain later.

124
00:12:16,891 --> 00:12:19,932
- Follow me.
- Yes, Your Highness.

125
00:12:26,286 --> 00:12:30,011
Why don't you visit the Royal Academy personally?

126
00:12:30,011 --> 00:12:34,049
It will help ease objections and encourage the scholars.

127
00:12:34,049 --> 00:12:37,412
You may also find the right candidate to serve at the Royal Library.

128
00:12:37,412 --> 00:12:41,907
My schedule is quite full, but I will consider it.

129
00:12:58,716 --> 00:13:00,289
Your Majesty.

130
00:13:01,883 --> 00:13:03,429
Your Majesty.

131
00:13:04,313 --> 00:13:08,424
Your Majesty? It is 8 o'clock.

132
00:13:12,982 --> 00:13:17,230
You commanded us to remind you.

133
00:13:20,913 --> 00:13:23,682
I have a lot to do, indeed.

134
00:13:43,013 --> 00:13:45,482
My apologies, Your Majesty.

135
00:13:45,482 --> 00:13:49,794
I did not expect your visit and failed to make suitable preparations.

136
00:13:49,794 --> 00:13:54,135
I came without notice. You need not apologize.

137
00:13:54,135 --> 00:13:59,730
Your Majesty... Actually, Queen Dowager is inside.

138
00:14:01,896 --> 00:14:04,136
Queen Dowager?

139
00:14:25,412 --> 00:14:27,605
Welcome, Your Majesty.

140
00:14:28,300 --> 00:14:31,396
Why is Sung Deok Im kneeling like that?

141
00:14:32,852 --> 00:14:35,629
Is this an interrogation?

142
00:14:35,629 --> 00:14:40,533
Yes, and we are about to begin.

143
00:14:44,685 --> 00:14:47,129
What crime is she accused of?

144
00:14:52,302 --> 00:14:56,330
It was reported that she has committed adultery.

145
00:15:00,418 --> 00:15:02,732
Is there any evidence?

146
00:15:03,496 --> 00:15:05,888
You will need evidence for such an accusation.

147
00:15:05,888 --> 00:15:08,123
- Hwabin.
- Yes, Your Highness.

148
00:15:08,123 --> 00:15:10,520
Show him the evidence.

149
00:15:10,520 --> 00:15:12,011
Yes.

150
00:15:41,674 --> 00:15:47,310
Is it true that you received this from an officer at the Royal Artillery?

151
00:15:47,310 --> 00:15:49,428
Yes, it is true.

152
00:15:50,190 --> 00:15:55,207
Sung Deok Im has met with this man regularly.

153
00:15:56,085 --> 00:16:01,007
She would give him food and medicine that she received at the palace.

154
00:16:01,007 --> 00:16:06,318
And on holidays, she would meet him alone.

155
00:16:06,318 --> 00:16:08,400
Is that true?

156
00:16:09,218 --> 00:16:11,175
It is.

157
00:16:11,175 --> 00:16:15,921
So you acknowledge seeing an army officer in privacy?

158
00:16:15,921 --> 00:16:17,017
I do.

159
00:16:17,017 --> 00:16:20,204
And you've exchanged presents and letters.

160
00:16:21,496 --> 00:16:23,327
We have.

161
00:16:23,327 --> 00:16:27,910
A court lady who has an affair with any man but the king,

162
00:16:27,910 --> 00:16:30,307
is punishable by death.

163
00:16:31,282 --> 00:16:33,125
Your Highness!

164
00:16:33,125 --> 00:16:35,500
What is it, Your Majesty?

165
00:16:36,042 --> 00:16:39,519
Is there anything you would like to add?

166
00:16:43,382 --> 00:16:47,515
I have something to discuss with him alone. Step outside for a moment.

167
00:16:47,515 --> 00:16:49,127
- Yes, Your Highness.
- Yes, Your Highenss...

168
00:17:13,508 --> 00:17:18,400
Your Majesty, I remember I once told you

169
00:17:18,400 --> 00:17:21,898
that there is nothing wrong in desiring something.

170
00:17:21,898 --> 00:17:26,320
As King, you may desire anything.

171
00:17:28,310 --> 00:17:33,810
Ask for this grandma's help and claim what you desire.

172
00:17:33,810 --> 00:17:37,191
Isn't there something that you so desperately desire?

173
00:17:48,917 --> 00:17:51,230
Adultery?

174
00:17:51,230 --> 00:17:54,609
Deok Im is under interrogation for adultery?

175
00:17:54,609 --> 00:17:56,301
What do we do, my lady?

176
00:17:56,301 --> 00:17:59,784
Concubine Hwabin must have framed her.

177
00:17:59,784 --> 00:18:00,890
An affair with whom?

178
00:18:00,890 --> 00:18:03,467
It's some army officer that just passed the exam.

179
00:18:03,467 --> 00:18:04,593
An officer?

180
00:18:04,593 --> 00:18:06,721
I heard there is evidence for it.

181
00:18:06,721 --> 00:18:11,151
- And they say that guy paid for the exam with the money Deok Im made by transcribing books.
- What?

182
00:18:11,151 --> 00:18:14,170
But that is nothing but a rumor.

183
00:18:14,170 --> 00:18:18,925
The man who passed the exam with her help?

184
00:18:22,114 --> 00:18:26,510
I-I have to go and talk to someone.

185
00:18:26,510 --> 00:18:31,604
Who are you talking to? Is it His Majesty?

186
00:18:32,675 --> 00:18:34,918
What will you do?

187
00:18:35,697 --> 00:18:40,796
Will you take the hand that I offer you?

188
00:18:40,796 --> 00:18:42,840
I won't.

189
00:18:44,970 --> 00:18:51,525
I could let my emotions guide me to act against the law and save her.

190
00:18:53,208 --> 00:18:56,505
- But I would be dishonoring all court ladies.
- How so?

191
00:18:56,505 --> 00:19:01,729
Those court ladies that are lofty and live in chastity,

192
00:19:02,982 --> 00:19:06,332
those devote their entire lives to the royal family.

193
00:19:07,806 --> 00:19:12,730
I cannot become a dishonorable king to them.

194
00:19:15,310 --> 00:19:17,760
You are indeed virtuous.

195
00:19:17,760 --> 00:19:20,290
What a great king you are.

196
00:19:21,403 --> 00:19:23,800
But you should also remember

197
00:19:24,603 --> 00:19:29,005
women do not like cold-hearted men.

198
00:19:29,618 --> 00:19:33,124
I thought you had quite some feelings for her.

199
00:19:33,124 --> 00:19:35,491
But now you will watch her die?

200
00:19:35,491 --> 00:19:40,880
I do not believe that she has committed adultery.

201
00:19:40,880 --> 00:19:42,615
She is not the sort!

202
00:19:42,615 --> 00:19:45,213
How naïve are you

203
00:19:46,015 --> 00:19:53,260
to believe that hundreds of court ladies will all be faithful to you.

204
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:55,238
Perhaps,

205
00:19:58,113 --> 00:20:01,380
she could have held feelings for another man.

206
00:20:01,380 --> 00:20:06,680
Even a king does not have control of what one desires at heart.

207
00:20:06,680 --> 00:20:12,418
So you would tolerate her harboring affection for another man?

208
00:20:13,504 --> 00:20:16,632
Well, I beg to differ.

209
00:20:16,632 --> 00:20:20,433
For me, loyalty is a top priority.

210
00:20:20,433 --> 00:20:26,215
Even if I like her, if she can't be mine,

211
00:20:26,215 --> 00:20:28,816
I would rather destroy her

212
00:20:29,488 --> 00:20:31,721
for getting on my nerves.

213
00:20:33,223 --> 00:20:36,307
I understand your intention.

214
00:20:36,307 --> 00:20:41,621
Even a king of one nation cannot save a mere court lady.

215
00:20:42,901 --> 00:20:47,800
Then, you can sit and watch as she dies.

216
00:20:55,294 --> 00:20:58,477
Bring in Sund Deok Im!

217
00:20:58,477 --> 00:21:00,940
Yes, Your Highness.

218
00:21:16,398 --> 00:21:18,127
Mother.

219
00:21:29,091 --> 00:21:32,700
Lady Hyegyeong, what brings you here?
(T/N: after King Jeongjo took the throne, her title changed from Princess Hyebin to Lady Hyegyeong)

220
00:21:32,700 --> 00:21:36,215
I heard there is a misunderstanding.

221
00:21:36,215 --> 00:21:37,599
A misunderstanding?

222
00:21:37,599 --> 00:21:41,524
I heard Deok Im is accused of adultery.

223
00:21:41,524 --> 00:21:43,804
Concubine Hwabin reported it.

224
00:21:43,804 --> 00:21:45,714
And she did not deny it.

225
00:21:45,714 --> 00:21:48,119
She didn't?

226
00:21:49,020 --> 00:21:53,016
She is merely being a good sister.

227
00:21:53,016 --> 00:21:54,210
Sister?

228
00:21:54,210 --> 00:21:58,518
Do you know who the officer is that she has allegedly been seeing?

229
00:21:58,518 --> 00:22:01,430
He is her brother.

230
00:22:02,600 --> 00:22:04,541
Brother?

231
00:22:05,189 --> 00:22:10,018
That cannot be true. Not according to what I've discovered.

232
00:22:11,482 --> 00:22:14,602
The name of the officer is Sung Sik.

233
00:22:14,602 --> 00:22:19,209
His last name may be Sung, but they do not share lineage.

234
00:22:19,209 --> 00:22:21,007
Hwabin,

235
00:22:21,007 --> 00:22:25,590
that is because this girl has been adopted by a servant of mine.

236
00:22:25,590 --> 00:22:27,560
Adopted?

237
00:22:30,687 --> 00:22:32,638
Your Highness,

238
00:22:32,638 --> 00:22:37,799
Deok Im's father was a royal guard at service of Prince Sado.

239
00:22:38,306 --> 00:22:43,140
When Prince Sado died, all of his royal guards were executed.

240
00:22:43,140 --> 00:22:46,940
That's when I rescued her and made her a palace maid.

241
00:22:48,185 --> 00:22:53,033
Sung Sik is indeed a blood brother of Sung Deok Im.

242
00:23:02,092 --> 00:23:04,527
He was your brother?

243
00:23:05,500 --> 00:23:08,088
Not knowing that, I…

244
00:23:09,988 --> 00:23:13,321
Why did you not tell the truth?

245
00:23:13,321 --> 00:23:16,540
You could've said so.

246
00:23:16,540 --> 00:23:19,308
Isn't it obvious, Your Majesty?

247
00:23:20,561 --> 00:23:23,480
If she were to reveal the fact that he is her biological brother,

248
00:23:23,480 --> 00:23:27,322
she must first reveal that they are children of a traitor.

249
00:23:27,322 --> 00:23:33,333
Then her brother would lose his position. That's why she couldn't say anything.

250
00:23:34,194 --> 00:23:37,633
Your Highness, this does not change anything.

251
00:23:37,633 --> 00:23:40,402
Please go ahead and punish Sung Deok Im.

252
00:23:40,402 --> 00:23:45,908
Although she has not committed adultery, she is the daughter of a traitor.

253
00:23:47,580 --> 00:23:50,325
Prince Sado was a sinner.

254
00:23:52,622 --> 00:23:58,716
- Sung Deok Im is a daughter of a traitor that served a sinner. Please behead—
- I am!

255
00:24:08,145 --> 00:24:10,913
I am the son of Prince Sado.

256
00:24:18,181 --> 00:24:20,460
My apologies, Your Majesty.

257
00:24:20,460 --> 00:24:23,570
I did not intend to insult you.

258
00:24:23,570 --> 00:24:26,921
Do you agree with Hwabin, Your Highness?

259
00:24:28,487 --> 00:24:31,918
Will you claim me an illegitimate king

260
00:24:32,491 --> 00:24:36,541
because I'm the son of Prince Sado?

261
00:24:41,705 --> 00:24:43,410
No.

262
