525
00:53:26,750 --> 00:53:31,650
If I do, will you let go of me?

526
00:53:31,650 --> 00:53:33,160
No.

527
00:53:59,890 --> 00:54:01,950
I've missed you.

528
00:54:04,206 --> 00:54:09,220
I thought you didn't visit me because you regretted that night.

529
00:54:09,220 --> 00:54:12,012
I should have come sooner

530
00:54:12,898 --> 00:54:16,040
if I had known you were having a silly thought.

531
00:54:23,411 --> 00:54:29,110
I thought… that you would need some time alone.

532
00:54:31,316 --> 00:54:35,280
Do you hate me for what I did?

533
00:54:35,280 --> 00:54:37,213
No.

534
00:54:37,925 --> 00:54:40,860
I've also missed Your Majesty.

535
00:54:41,895 --> 00:54:43,698
Is that true?

536
00:54:47,194 --> 00:54:50,106
From now on, you will always be by my side.

537
00:54:51,318 --> 00:54:53,502
For you are mine.

538
00:54:54,689 --> 00:54:59,013
Yes. I am yours.

539
00:55:00,802 --> 00:55:05,623
But you cannot ever entirely be mine.

540
00:55:06,705 --> 00:55:09,199
Don't give me that look.

541
00:55:10,613 --> 00:55:12,622
Why do you say that?

542
00:55:12,622 --> 00:55:18,160
You… look like you're thinking about running away.

543
00:55:28,900 --> 00:55:30,920
That will be of no use.

544
00:55:32,002 --> 00:55:34,505
I will never let you go.

545
00:56:21,312 --> 00:56:26,214
Factions shouldn't matter in any way.

546
00:56:26,214 --> 00:56:29,403
I expected political balance from all of you.

547
00:56:29,403 --> 00:56:33,327
You are neither narrow-minded people nor little children in the streets!

548
00:56:33,327 --> 00:56:36,750
Until when do I have to reconcile the two factions?

549
00:56:42,399 --> 00:56:46,196
We are honored, Your Majesty.

550
00:56:46,196 --> 00:56:50,414
We are honored, Your Majesty.

551
00:56:59,992 --> 00:57:04,316
If you visit me during the day, the officials will issue an appeal.

552
00:57:06,114 --> 00:57:09,110
I just came to catch my breath.

553
00:57:12,796 --> 00:57:15,215
This feels better.

554
00:57:16,999 --> 00:57:19,620
Are you tired?

555
00:57:23,106 --> 00:57:24,809
A little bit…

556
00:57:28,003 --> 00:57:30,896
What have you been doing all day?

557
00:57:33,597 --> 00:57:36,630
I've done nothing special.

558
00:57:37,200 --> 00:57:41,891
I but sit here waiting for you.

559
00:57:41,891 --> 00:57:44,101
That is my part.

560
00:57:50,300 --> 00:57:53,212
I like lying on your lap.

561
00:57:53,212 --> 00:57:57,640
And my legs have to do the hard work for that.

562
00:58:00,586 --> 00:58:03,093
Why do you smile?

563
00:58:03,093 --> 00:58:05,013
Because I'm enjoying this.

564
00:58:07,413 --> 00:58:11,625
I mean it's good to be slacking off.

565
00:58:13,093 --> 00:58:18,490
I wish we could stay like this forever.

566
00:59:08,008 --> 00:59:10,690
Did you have a bad dream?

567
00:59:19,721 --> 00:59:21,190
You…

568
00:59:23,400 --> 00:59:25,400
you're here.

569
00:59:27,203 --> 00:59:29,780
I have been here all along.

570
00:59:29,780 --> 00:59:33,450
You've been sleeping all day long on my lap.

571
00:59:56,504 --> 01:00:00,811
You should go now. This is too long a break.

572
01:00:02,902 --> 01:00:04,600
Yes.

573
01:00:05,860 --> 01:00:07,520
I will.

574
01:00:23,506 --> 01:00:24,898
Deok Im.

575
01:00:24,898 --> 01:00:26,940
Yes, Your Majesty.

576
01:00:28,431 --> 01:00:34,180
I will never love as my grandfather did.

577
01:00:34,180 --> 01:00:35,312
Pardon?

578
01:00:35,312 --> 01:00:38,014
I will do anything

579
01:00:40,313 --> 01:00:42,702
to protect the one I love.

580
01:00:44,508 --> 01:00:47,360
What are you speaking of?

581
01:00:49,998 --> 01:00:53,297
I see. Please, return.

582
01:00:53,297 --> 01:00:55,880
You are actually late.

583
01:01:22,516 --> 01:01:26,280
Are you not having your period?

584
01:01:26,800 --> 01:01:28,096
No.

585
01:01:28,096 --> 01:01:31,650
Could you be… pregnant?

586
01:01:32,214 --> 01:01:38,217
It's not certain. So I haven't told His Majesty yet.

587
01:01:38,217 --> 01:01:41,499
I want to wait until it is confirmed.

588
01:01:41,499 --> 01:01:44,480
Then you can't be in bed with him.

589
01:01:44,480 --> 01:01:47,620
Doesn't he visit you every day? Would you be all right?

590
01:02:07,892 --> 01:02:11,920
His Majesty is on his way!

591
01:02:17,588 --> 01:02:21,861
Your Majesty, I sent word that I cannot be with you tonight.

592
01:02:21,861 --> 01:02:25,284
I heard you were sick. That's why I came to see you.

593
01:02:26,507 --> 01:02:31,229
You don't look pale or anything.

594
01:02:31,229 --> 01:02:36,198
Tell me about your symptoms. I have read many medical texts. I know quite a lot about illnesses.

595
01:02:36,198 --> 01:02:38,170
What are they?

596
01:02:39,096 --> 01:02:41,340
Well…

597
01:02:41,340 --> 01:02:44,510
- I have the chills...
- Chills?

598
01:02:46,193 --> 01:02:48,840
You don't have a fever.

599
01:02:50,103 --> 01:02:52,902
- I'm dizzy.
- Dizzy?

600
01:02:52,902 --> 01:02:55,280
Walk a few steps.

601
01:03:07,915 --> 01:03:10,220
That's weird.

602
01:03:15,001 --> 01:03:20,022
Perhaps... Did you happen to feign illness

603
01:03:20,022 --> 01:03:22,512
because you didn't want me here?

604
01:03:22,512 --> 01:03:24,892
I didn't.

605
01:03:24,892 --> 01:03:28,025
I don't think you're sick at all.

606
01:03:28,750 --> 01:03:31,920
Did you not want me? Is that it?

607
01:03:31,920 --> 01:03:35,774
Your Majesty, are you so fond of me?

608
01:03:35,774 --> 01:03:36,684
What?

609
01:03:36,684 --> 01:03:41,125
Would you fall ill if you don't see me even for a day?

610
01:03:41,125 --> 01:03:44,630
Hey! You…

611
01:03:46,010 --> 01:03:47,604
Right.

612
01:03:47,604 --> 01:03:52,086
You must actually be sick since you're talking nonsense.

613
01:03:52,086 --> 01:03:55,510
I will give you the perfect prescription.

614
01:03:58,909 --> 01:04:01,320
Drink some cold water

615
01:04:01,320 --> 01:04:03,500
and go to bed.

616
01:04:12,809 --> 01:04:14,412
Your Majesty.

617
01:04:17,494 --> 01:04:21,220
Are you not returning to your palace?

618
01:04:21,220 --> 01:04:25,707
Do you want me to walk back there when it's so late?

619
01:04:25,707 --> 01:04:29,480
I am actually not feeling well…

620
01:04:29,480 --> 01:04:33,750
What are you thinking? I'm not going to do anything.

621
01:04:45,497 --> 01:04:49,628
Tonight I will simply hold your hand. That's all.

622
01:04:49,628 --> 01:04:51,819
Are you sure?

623
01:06:19,905 --> 01:06:23,726
You are indeed pregnant. Congratulations, Your Highness.

624
01:06:26,408 --> 01:06:28,623
Be careful.

625
01:06:30,791 --> 01:06:33,210
Congratulations, Your Highness.

626
01:06:33,210 --> 01:06:36,440
Congratulations, Your Highness.

627
01:06:44,087 --> 01:06:46,990
We have to share the news with Court Lady Seo.

628
01:06:47,637 --> 01:06:50,119
And with His Majesty.

629
01:06:50,119 --> 01:06:51,602
He will be so happy.

630
01:06:51,602 --> 01:06:54,320
He will be beyond happy.

631
01:06:58,000 --> 01:06:58,699
Pregnant?

632
01:06:58,699 --> 01:07:03,008
Yes, Your Majesty. Court Lady Sung is pregnant.

633
01:07:03,108 --> 01:07:07,519
Does she indeed bear my child?

634
01:07:07,519 --> 01:07:12,650
Yes. A royal nurse confirmed so.

635
01:07:25,800 --> 01:07:27,720
What am I doing here?

636
01:07:27,720 --> 01:07:29,360
Please watch your steps.

637
01:07:29,360 --> 01:07:32,050
- Hurry. Follow me.
- Yes, Your Majesty.

638
01:07:42,088 --> 01:07:43,591
Your Majesty.

639
01:08:02,623 --> 01:08:05,323
I thought you were going to the annex.

640
01:08:23,910 --> 01:08:26,310
What is that purse?

641
01:08:27,803 --> 01:08:29,318
Nothing…

642
01:08:33,703 --> 01:08:36,235
When is His Majesty coming?

643
01:08:37,003 --> 01:08:38,040
He must be busy.

644
01:08:38,040 --> 01:08:42,606
Still, he has to come to see you on a day like this.

645
01:08:45,311 --> 01:08:47,602
He will come soon.

646
01:08:50,498 --> 01:08:53,920
Court Lady Sung, this is the Head of the Royal Guard.

647
01:09:08,006 --> 01:09:11,003
His Majesty wanted me to deliver a message.

648
01:09:11,003 --> 01:09:15,816
He cannot visit you tonight, so you shouldn't wait.

649
01:09:17,224 --> 01:09:20,015
How can he not come on a day like this?

650
01:09:20,015 --> 01:09:23,475
Does he not know that Court Lady Sung is pregnant?

651
01:09:23,475 --> 01:09:25,401
This cannot be.

652
01:09:25,401 --> 01:09:29,144
But it's not my fault that he can't come.

653
01:09:29,144 --> 01:09:33,241
My lady here has waited all day.

654
01:09:33,241 --> 01:09:37,370
Well… I didn't stop him from coming here.

655
01:09:37,370 --> 01:09:39,690
He's just…

656
01:09:39,690 --> 01:09:44,796
I am the captain. You're not supposed to treat me like this.

657
01:09:44,796 --> 01:09:49,760
I will explain this to Court Lady Sung.

658
01:09:57,322 --> 01:10:00,724
Congratulations on your pregnancy.

659
01:10:04,114 --> 01:10:05,791
You should go now.

660
01:10:05,791 --> 01:10:08,360
Then I'll leave you to it.

661
01:10:11,593 --> 01:10:13,920
You should leave, as well.

662
01:10:13,920 --> 01:10:15,895
- Yes.
- Yes.

663
01:10:35,687 --> 01:10:40,619
Deok Im, what a blessing this is.

664
01:10:40,619 --> 01:10:42,811
It truly is one.

665
01:10:43,986 --> 01:10:48,230
Can His Majesty not come?

666
01:10:55,009 --> 01:10:59,212
He is with the Queen.

667
01:10:59,212 --> 01:11:03,301
He will stay there tonight.

668
01:11:04,391 --> 01:11:09,836
Her Highness has wanted a child for so long,

669
01:11:09,836 --> 01:11:12,619
but that never happened.

670
01:11:14,071 --> 01:11:18,011
It only took you three months to get pregnant since you were officially favored by His Majesty.

671
01:11:18,011 --> 01:11:21,519
How do you think Her Highness would feel?

672
01:11:22,992 --> 01:11:28,217
He has to visit and comfort her.

673
01:11:29,102 --> 01:11:35,270
It is his rightful duty and responsibility as King.

674
01:11:36,500 --> 01:11:40,824
I understand, my lady,

675
01:11:42,097 --> 01:11:48,324
that the Queen has to be in his top priority, not me.

676
01:11:49,690 --> 01:11:54,360
I already knew I should not desire anything or

677
01:11:54,360 --> 01:11:57,422
expect anything from His Majesty

678
01:11:58,389 --> 01:12:03,110
from the beginning.

679
01:13:11,701 --> 01:13:13,695
You're here.

680
01:13:13,695 --> 01:13:16,350
I didn't mean to wake you.

681
01:13:25,386 --> 01:13:27,927
I am glad you came.

682
01:13:29,894 --> 01:13:32,457
I'm sorry I couldn't come yesterday.

683
01:13:32,457 --> 01:13:34,412
Don't be.

684
01:13:35,619 --> 01:13:38,533
I thought you would be disappointed.

685
01:13:38,533 --> 01:13:41,380
It is not your fault.

686
01:13:43,689 --> 01:13:45,570
Have you heard?

687
01:13:46,430 --> 01:13:48,600
I have your child.

688
01:13:48,600 --> 01:13:53,617
Yes. I was so glad to hear that.

689
01:13:55,982 --> 01:13:58,638
Do you wish it'd be a son?

690
01:13:59,694 --> 01:14:02,800
Am I asking something so obvious?

691
01:14:05,420 --> 01:14:11,493
A daughter like you will be a clueless tomboy.

692
01:14:11,493 --> 01:14:14,107
How would I handle her?

693
01:14:21,099 --> 01:14:22,900
Still…

694
01:14:23,610 --> 01:14:28,332
she would be lovely, just like you.

695
01:14:30,795 --> 01:14:35,904
Be it a mature son, or a reckless daughter,

696
01:14:37,701 --> 01:14:40,194
I'll be truly happy.

697
01:14:41,008 --> 01:14:46,714
With our child, we will truly become family.

698
01:14:49,322 --> 01:14:56,950
Have you ever wished to be a common man, not a king?

699
01:15:01,623 --> 01:15:03,616
Well.

700
01:15:06,987 --> 01:15:09,923
I've never thought about that.

701
01:15:11,393 --> 01:15:14,850
I sometimes wonder,

702
01:15:15,417 --> 01:15:21,109
what if I were not a court lady, and you not a king?

703
01:15:22,295 --> 01:15:28,500
How would it be if we were to meet as commoners?

704
01:15:34,724 --> 01:15:37,111
I'm not so sure...

705
01:15:38,298 --> 01:15:40,896
I cannot imagine.

706
01:15:48,289 --> 01:15:51,309
It suits you to be a court lady.

707
01:15:54,893 --> 01:16:01,320
Indeed. And it suits you to be king.

708
01:16:20,095 --> 01:16:22,031
Your Majesty.

709
01:16:23,594 --> 01:16:28,177
We have heard that your concubine got pregnant.

710
01:16:28,177 --> 01:16:30,014
Congratulations.

711
01:16:30,014 --> 01:16:33,070
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

712
01:16:34,396 --> 01:16:38,396
Thank you all.

713
01:16:40,081 --> 01:16:46,660
It would have been even better if it were the Queen.

714
01:16:50,806 --> 01:16:56,404
But it is good enough that you have an heir.

715
01:16:56,404 --> 01:16:58,127
Congratulations.

716
01:16:58,127 --> 01:17:03,467
Thank you, Assistant Counselor. I'm so happy.

717
01:17:04,486 --> 01:17:08,706
Hey, Assistant Counselor. Aren't you happy, too?

718
01:17:08,706 --> 01:17:14,440
Oh, of course, I am, Your Majesty.

719
01:17:15,334 --> 01:17:18,298
Then perhaps you should laugh harder!

720
01:17:23,189 --> 01:17:25,450
Laugh louder.

721
01:17:37,617 --> 01:17:40,622
Don't you really need anything?

722
01:17:40,622 --> 01:17:44,192
I can procure anything through my father.

723
01:17:44,192 --> 01:17:46,330
I don't need anything.

724
01:17:46,330 --> 01:17:49,770
And please talk to me like a friend.

725
01:17:49,770 --> 01:17:52,326
It gives me chills whenever you talk to me formally.

726
01:17:52,326 --> 01:17:58,738
We cannot do that. You now bear His Majesty's child.

727
01:17:58,738 --> 01:18:01,523
Things are different.

728
01:18:01,523 --> 01:18:07,420
But remember that, at heart, we will always be your friend.

729
01:18:10,019 --> 01:18:13,709
It's been a while since our last vacation together.

730
01:18:13,709 --> 01:18:17,523
It's too bad you can't join us, Your Highness.

731
01:18:17,523 --> 01:18:22,908
You know well. I cannot set foot outside the palace forever.

732
01:18:22,908 --> 01:18:27,180
Now, I'm destined to live here all my life.

733
01:18:28,600 --> 01:18:34,029
It's fine. I have you guys. You can see everything outside the walls for me

734
01:18:34,029 --> 01:18:37,730
and tell me when you return.

735
01:19:11,603 --> 01:19:13,297
Guys!

736
01:19:16,191 --> 01:19:19,120
You're late!

737
01:19:19,120 --> 01:19:21,624
Hey.

738
01:19:21,624 --> 01:19:23,095
Let's go.

739
01:19:23,095 --> 01:19:24,995
What do you want to eat?

740
01:19:24,995 --> 01:19:28,440
It's been a while since I went outside. I want something good.

741
01:19:28,440 --> 01:19:31,110
What should we have?

742
01:19:45,095 --> 01:19:46,718
Deok Im!

743
01:20:34,201 --> 01:20:37,416
As I spend more and more time in this room by myself,

744
01:20:37,416 --> 01:20:41,216
I keep thinking about

745
01:20:42,019 --> 01:20:46,020
what I have gained in my time here

746
01:20:47,716 --> 01:20:51,870
and… what I have lost.

747
01:21:02,840 --> 01:21:05,570
[Ui]

748
01:21:15,410 --> 01:21:17,415
Oh, you're up.

749
01:21:18,686 --> 01:21:20,818
When did you come here?

750
01:21:21,993 --> 01:21:25,508
Stay seated. No need to stand up.

751
01:21:25,508 --> 01:21:29,103
- But how could I?
- It's fine.
(T/N: A person with a higher rank is supposed to sit inside)

752
01:21:34,840 --> 01:21:37,870
[Many different Chinese characters]

753
01:21:37,870 --> 01:21:40,184
What have you written down?

754
01:21:40,184 --> 01:21:42,500
A character I will bestow on you.
(T/N: Name for her new title as a concubine)

755
01:21:44,693 --> 01:21:47,618
You're pregnant.

756
01:21:47,618 --> 01:21:52,390
If you give birth to a son, you will officially become a bin.
(T/N: the most senior rank for concubines)

757
01:21:56,498 --> 01:21:59,330
I have decided on a name.

758
01:21:59,330 --> 01:22:01,680
[Ui]

759
01:22:01,680 --> 01:22:04,220
"Ui" meaning "appropriate."

760
01:22:06,098 --> 01:22:08,804
But why this character?

761
01:22:08,804 --> 01:22:11,815
Wait. Don't you like it?

762
01:22:11,815 --> 01:22:15,513
It's weird that you're giving me such a good one.

763
01:22:15,513 --> 01:22:18,250
It's not like you.

764
01:22:18,250 --> 01:22:22,780
Then… what character do you think I would give you?

765
01:22:22,780 --> 01:22:28,390
It could be "Mungbin" for "a stupid concubine"...

766
01:22:28,390 --> 01:22:33,660
Or "Gwaebin" for "weirdo"...

767
01:22:33,660 --> 01:22:39,227
If such characters existed, they would be perfect for you.

768
01:22:39,227 --> 01:22:44,640
Tell me. Why did you pick this character?

769
01:22:47,298 --> 01:22:50,899
Do you know the expression "Ui-ga-ui-sil"?

770
01:22:50,899 --> 01:22:54,393
It means "to live in harmony as husband and wife."

771
01:22:54,393 --> 01:22:58,193
Do you know the expression "Ui-ga-ji-rak"?

772
01:22:58,193 --> 01:23:01,635
It means "to live in joy as husband and wife."

773
01:23:03,015 --> 01:23:08,900
That's why I'm giving you the character "ui."

774
01:23:10,103 --> 01:23:15,800
I told you that I want to have a family with you.

775
01:23:22,085 --> 01:23:26,927
Doesn't "ui" also mean "to like"?

776
01:23:30,101 --> 01:23:31,934
Is that right?

777
01:23:34,490 --> 01:23:37,012
So you already know.

778
01:23:39,195 --> 01:23:40,810
You…

779
01:23:43,060 --> 01:23:46,310
once told me

780
01:23:46,310 --> 01:23:51,024
that you would never truly love me.

781
01:23:55,609 --> 01:23:57,814
Do you still think so?

782
01:24:26,904 --> 01:24:29,006
It doesn't matter.

783
01:24:30,203 --> 01:24:33,098
After all, you're mine.

784
01:24:38,622 --> 01:24:43,903
I may be happy today, but sad on another.

785
01:24:43,903 --> 01:24:49,016
Perhaps, that's what life is all about.

786
01:24:49,016 --> 01:24:54,370
It will be both sad and happy.

787
01:24:55,680 --> 01:24:59,330
I'm happy that you're giving me a good name.

788
01:25:00,140 --> 01:25:02,814
Shall I make you happy, as well?

789
01:25:13,403 --> 01:25:15,604
Do you feel it?

790
01:25:20,894 --> 01:25:23,328
I do.

791
01:25:23,328 --> 01:25:26,408
There is no way you can already feel it.

792
01:25:29,685 --> 01:25:32,411
No, I really do feel it.

